      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in an impeccable state, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior luster, adheres to the highest aesthetic and mechanical benchmarks. Rigorously inspected to ensure showroom-grade performance, this offering represents a definitive acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
